response.original_title: Leslie Sansone: The Big Burn: 2 Miles of Intervals
response.overview: Get ready to boost your brisk walk to a boosted walk with intervals of walking and jogging that really work to increase calorie burn. It's easy to do in small doses - walk a little, jog a little - 2 miles will go by in a snap!  "The Big Burn" includes all the classic features of "Walk At Home" workouts:  A warm up walk A brisk 4, 5 and 5.5 mph pace Mile markers that allow you to choose 1 or 2 miles Multi-muscle moves A cool down walk and healthy stretch to end
response.title: Leslie Sansone: The Big Burn: 2 Miles of Intervals
